Moved message helper function to qquickwindowprivate.cpp as Gunnar suggested. 

What about the enumerations in QQuickWidget? 

It has Status (mirroring QQmlComponent/QQuickView::Status) and this change adds SceneGraphError (mirroring QuickWindow::SceneGraphError). Since it also includes QuickWindow, we could use QuickWindow::SceneGraphError, but it might be bit awkward when writing connections (see https://codereview.qt-project.org/#change,79990 ).

The doc bot is silent here due to Task-number: QTBUG-37272
